data.description: Welcome to 2346 Balmoral Drive, a grand cul-de-sac residence in Henderson. This expansive 4-bedroom, 3 full and 2 half-bathroom home boasts two living areas, multiple sitting areas, and a sprawling enclosed rear sunroom that spans the entire length of the home. Step onto the inviting front porch and enter through the grand foyer with high ceilings. To your left, a formal living room or office space awaits, while the formal dining room is to your right. Moving past a convenient half bath, discover the family room with an updated tiled fireplace and a wet bar. The kitchen, adorned with brand new granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, comfortably accommodates a table for six. A walk-in pantry and an additional half bath lead to a hallway connecting the utility room and the two-car garage. On the main level, a small study and the owner’s suite beckon, featuring a spacious sitting area, a walk-in closet, and a full bath. Ascend the stairs to find another ensuite with a walk-in closet and a private bath. An overlook down to the foyer provides a cozy seating area and leads to two more bedrooms and a full bath. A sizable storage room off the overlook adds practicality to the layout. Don't overlook the impressive sunroom stretching a generous 50 feet across the back of the home. Recent updates, including main level flooring, granite countertops, interior and exterior paint, light fixtures, sunroom flooring, and added insulation, enhance the home's allure. Move-in ready just in time for the holiday season, this residence invites you to make it your own.
